### ========================================================
### Public Relations Contact System
### ========================================================

### Contact - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contacts
Accept: application/json

### Contact - GET BY ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/1
Accept: application/json

### Contact - GET BY COMPANY
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/company/Ironhack
Accept: application/json

### Contact - GET BY TITLE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/title/Manager
Accept: application/json

### Contact - POST
POST http://localhost:8080/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "company": "New Company",
  "title": "Director",
  "name": {
    "salutation": "Mr.",
    "firstName": "John",
    "middleName": "A.",
    "lastName": "Doe"
  }
}

### Contact - PUT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "company": "Updated Company",
  "title": "Senior Director",
  "name": {
    "salutation": "Mr.",
    "firstName": "John",
    "middleName": "B.",
    "lastName": "Updated"
  }
}

### Contact - PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Chief Manager"
}

### Contact - DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/contacts/1
Accept: application/json